'''Mother Teresa''' zaun asli ek [[Katolik]] madr. Ti Eropan zolmoleli, pun aplem akhem jivit tinnem Indien sarli, dubleanchi, goribanchi, piddentachi ani mortoleanchi seva korun. Tinnem ''Missionaries of Charity'', ho ordr chalu kelo, zo techo ho vavr fuddem vorta. Tika Nobel Puroskar ui favo zalo.

Modor terezhachem purai namv aegonesa gonxa bozaxiyu. Tichea bapaichem namv nikola bozaxiyu ani auychem dranafile (drondda)bernai. Aegnes egsotachea 26ver 1910 vorsa yugosolavia albaniachea skopji kheddeant zolmak aili. Dus-ya disa tika bautijm' dilo. Tim sogllim mellun panch bhamvdda. Aegones modlentacho vhoddlo bhavo lazar foujent riglo. Tachi uprantoli bhoinn aez xikpak khub huxar asli. Tinnem orthoxasrotacho obheas kelo. Aegonesa uprantcheo dog bhoinni lhanuch astana somvsarak ontorleo. Aegonesa at vorsanchem astona tacho bapuy somplo. Xivon sut ani hatan kel'leo vostu vikun tanche auyn kuttumbachem udaroposon kelem। punn teach borobor tinne aplem dhormikoponn soddle na। igorjechea gaupea pongddant vantto gheun toxench piddeuntank ani gorjeuntank pavunk ti poili asli। tichem ghor ek dhormik kendr zal'lem।ho tichea xeguni jivitacho probhavo aplea dhuvancherui zalo। egnes ani ez deva peleacheamogan vaddlim।[1]

egnesan aplem bhurgeponn heram bhurgeam bhoxen samany ritin sarlem। padvigarachea toxench aplea xikxokanchea margodrxona khal tem nit ani thir xikxon ghetalem। dusroya pasot taka ek vhodd husko aslo। [2]

egnes bara vorsanche zale ten'na aplea apounea vixim nirnnoi gheupacho aslo। egnes aplea igrjent soddeliti amf do blesod vorzon meri he soumsthechi ek hurbeunt vangddi asli।tancho padvigar aplea sfurt divpi adexaurovim ti somstha choloitalo ani vangddeank margodrxon ditalo। hea sfurt divpi ulouvpam vorvim egnesachea dublleam pasot mog nirman zalo। tem aplea kallzant ek mixeonarin zaupachi amvddo posovunk lagli।jen'n tinnem aplo nirnnoi aple auyk kolloilo ten'n survatek tika apli dhuv ghor soddun gel'li naka asli।punn teach borobor devache khoxe addui tem gel'lem tika naka aslem। gombhirotayen vichar korun auyn aple dhuvek ticho hat devachea hatant ghalunk tachea sangatak cholunk budhd dili। egnesan otthra vorsanche pirayer devachea apounnoya khatir apnnachem atmosomrponn kelem। egnesacher thoddea tornatea jezhuit mixiyonarancho probhavo boslo। te bengolant kam' kortale te suttyenk aplea gamvghora porotl'le kodden tanni egnesak ,koloktt'ttant ani her suvater loretto madri jeo mixionari vaur kortaleo te vixim sogllem barikosannen sanglem। hea vellar egnesachea kallzant te somsthent rigpacho amvddovo rujlo। nouhemborachea 29ver 1928 vorsa egnes loretto vorgant bhitor sorli। egnesan ailenddachea rathfarnham' hangasor loretto vorgant dhormik khaxelea xikxonnachem ek vors sopoilem। uprant taka bengaloche vixixtt dhormokarea khatir venchun kaddli। tum-i tem 1929ant zanerachea 6ver gelem। [3] xeuttim

